<div class="product-grid-item js-product-wrapper js-grid-product " data-title="SuperSuede™ Baked Powder Blush" data-price="28.00" data-variant="44189867475120" data-product-handle="supersuede">

  
  <script type="application/json" class="js-product-data" data-id="7782814384304" data-handle="supersuede">
    {"id":7782814384304,"title":"SuperSuede™ Baked Powder Blush","handle":"supersuede","description":"\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuper luxurious and super plush, SuperSuede™ Baked Powder Blush is the new standard for baked powder blush. Hand-whipped and baked using time-honored Italian techniques, SuperSuede™ has a velvety texture that melts into skin for an impossibly lightweight, diffused \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eflush of color\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a natural-blurred finish. With a curated palette of six shades, SuperSuede™ Blush gives effortless, breathable color payoff, and works for a wide range of looks. SuperSuede™ is also non-comedogenic, long-wearing, and never patchy, cakey, or drying.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003ePair with NEW: \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.saiehello.com\/products\/the-powder-blush-brush\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Powder Blush Brush\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e, intentionally designed for SuperSuede™ for precise, seamless application.  \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWe recommend keeping SuperSuede™ out of direct lighting, both natural and artificial, when not in use. Since this formula contains some light-sensitive pigments, excess light may affect the top layer. Simply dust off the top layer to return to normal.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2025-02-20T00:00:05-05:00","created_at":"2025-02-03T16:08:52-05:00","vendor":"Saie","type":"Makeup","tags":["badge:new","cheek","face","new","tyb"],"price":2800,"price_min":2800,"price_max":2800,"available":true,"price_varies":false,"compare_at_price":null,"compare_at_price_min":0,"compare_at_price_max":0,"compare_at_price_varies":false,"variants":[{"id":44189867573424,"title":"Amore","option1":"Amore","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"SDWB05GBL","requires_shippi