,"description":null,"options":[{"name":"Deliver every","position":1,"value":"4 months"}],"recurring_deliveries":true,"price_adjustments":[{"order_count":null,"position":1,"value_type":"percentage","value":10}],"checkout_charge":{"value_type":"percentage","value":100}}],"app_id":"5859381"}],"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003c!-- x-tinymce\/html --\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"sh-color-black sh-color\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003eDew Blush™ is sure to be your holy-grail essential for an effortless flush. With its blendable, liquid-cream formula and chunky doe-foot applicator, Dew Blush™ melts seamlessly into cheeks for a dewy wash of color. This lightweight, skin-loving formula lets you create a natural tint or build for a deeper wash of color that's never streaky or patchy. Now available in 11 shades for a wide range of complexions to find their perfect flush. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDew Blush™  is safe for \u003cstrong\u003esensitive skin, fragrance free, cruelty free, formulated without gluten and vegan. \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e"}
