dir=\"ltr\"\u003eThe slip of a lip oil meets the high-shine of a tinted gloss. Glossybounce™ is our best-selling, high-shine lip gloss-oil hybrid with a plush, cushiony feel that’s never sticky or tacky. This long-lasting, vegan lip essential is supercharged with nourishing, hydrating ingredients for soft lips and your juiciest shine ever!Available in \u003cstrong class=\"sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003enine\u003c\/strong\u003e sheer shades and three shimmer shades. Get a Glossybounce™ for every bag!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eGlossybounce™ is formulated without natural or synthetic fragrance and with a touch of natural stevia for taste. You may notice the scent of raw ingredients but this fades quickly after application\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e"}
  </script>

